name: I am a lemon pt. 2
description: The depths of the lemon have reached the part of your body that makes you stand tall in this society: your spine. Every part of your body is supported by the lemon that gives you freedom. You are bold. The affirmation words are an important process of accepting yourself: I am a lemon, even if sometimes I don’t feel like it. ‘I am a lemon pt.2’ is the fifth nft in the second part of the lemon collection. The second part of the lemon collection tells the rest of the story in 6 illustrations. This part is about becoming and sharing the lemon. Digital artwork made in 2021 by Camila Trapasso (camamblo).
